Steps to implement:

1. Download Roboto-Bold.ttf from Google Fonts:
   https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Roboto
   Select the Bold (700) weight variant

2. Place the downloaded Roboto-Bold.ttf file in:
   src/ios/ios/Fonts/Roboto-Bold.ttf

3. Verify the file has the following properties:
   - Format: TrueType Font (.ttf)
   - Family: Roboto
   - Weight: 700 (Bold)
   - Style: Normal
   - Version: Latest stable release
   - License: Apache License 2.0

4. Add font to Info.plist:
   <key>UIAppFonts</key>
   <array>
       <string>Roboto-Bold.ttf</string>
   </array>

5. Reference in typography.ts:
   export const FONT_BOLD = "Roboto-Bold"

Font specifications:
- Supports iOS 12.0+
- Optimized for Retina displays
- Includes full Unicode character set
- Supports Dynamic Type
- Pre-compiled for optimal performance